  "keyFeatures": [
    "On-device audio generation via Apple Silicon Metal GPU — no cloud API required",
    "MusicGen support: mono, stereo, melody-conditioned, and style-conditioned variants",
    "Stable Audio Open: diffusion-based stereo generation at 44.1 kHz",
    "Demucs v4 stem separation: drums, bass, vocals, and other",
    "CLI, HTTP server, React web UI, VST3/AU plugin, and Max for Live integration",
    "AI prompt enhancement via local LLM (mlx-lm)",
    "LoRA fine-tuning support for MusicGen",
    "MIDI export and MIDI-to-prompt conversion"
